        </p>
      </section>

      <Map client:load />

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-slate-800 text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
          The day of your flight
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-800">
          Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting
